perf version: Append 12 git SHA chars to the version string

Bumping it from just 4:

Before:

  $ perf -v
  perf version 5.2.rc1.g80978f
  $

After:

  $ perf -v
  perf version 5.2.rc1.g80978fc864c5
  $

